1. Installation on Linux


1.1. Prerequisites
Go (Golang): Make sure you have Go installed. You can install it via your package manager or download it from golang.org.


 --> Using Go

 --> Set up Go environment:
  export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/go/bin
  export GOPATH=$HOME/go
  export PATH=$PATH:$GOPATH/bin

 --> Install Ffuf:
go install github.com/ffuf/ffuf/v2@latest

--> Verify Installation:
ffuf -h


